      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Sacrilegious Thunder Wolf",
        "Client": "Strong-legged Lady",
        "Description": "I hike up the mountain every day\r\nto pray in the Shrine Ruins, but\r\nthe other day I spotted a brilliant\r\nflash, and wouldn\u0027t you know it,\r\na Zinogre\u0027s taken up shop there!\r\nI can\u0027t go pray if that beastie\u0027s\r\nup there! Go get rid of it!",
